{"tid":142588,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"生田斗真化身男老師譜禁忌戀「課後輔導」撩妹超心動","createTime":"2017-03-04T02:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T07:02:59.000Z","uid":9573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e73f4fe3ee1a0f9bc282858b4d60357bcf398de6","tid":142588,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"日本傑尼斯男星生田斗真外型帥氣、戲路多變，主演的作品幾乎部部爆紅，在繼電影《當他們認真編織時》扮演跨性別者之後，他又重返帥氣形象準備撩妹，在新作《老師！》中飾演男老師，並與女主角廣瀨鈴展開禁忌師生戀。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2370/d2370116.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2370%2Fd2370116.jpg&h=2acd6056&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲生田斗真在新戲中與廣瀨鈴發展師生戀。<br />\n<br />\n生田斗真在《老師！》片中的世界史老師伊藤貢作，在與前女友分開後變得不信任女性，因細心又負責的性格，讓沒有戀愛經驗的學生島田響（廣瀨鈴飾）動心。電影預告開頭，廣瀨鈴就大聲告白：「老師，我可以喜歡你嗎？」中間穿插許多女主角對於老師的單相思情節及互動；再加上生田所飾演的男老師充滿成熟男人的帥氣，讓女網友直呼：「根本是會走路的賀爾蒙！」作品備受期待。《老師！》10月28日將在日本上映。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2370/d2370117.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2370%2Fd2370117.jpg&h=e66760c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/rPvc1o0qleA/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FrPvc1o0qleA%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=d94bd865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2370/d2370118.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2370%2Fd2370118.jpg&h=3f477264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲預告中有生田斗真為廣瀨鈴課後輔導的場景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Lr8L7rMpeSY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLr8L7rMpeSY&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZmMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=f56def85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Lr8L7rMpeSY</a>"},{"pid":"6e32fb6508ed5ef18695a61cefbfe09042c60c94","tid":142588,"uid":13638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"殊殊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lo